REALTY TV star, actress and model, Thandi “Blue” Mbombo is pregnant with her first baby. She announced the news on her social media platforms on Monday, 14 February. The former Big Brother Mzansi contestant shared a video clip of herself, riding a luxurious vintage Mercedes-Benz. The video clip was accompanied by a caption which read: “The most perfect Valentine’s gift. Thank you Lord #mom2b #ValentinesDay 2022.” In another, post she wrote: “We plan but God decides. This is an eternal love I’ve longed and prayed for all my life. Thank you Lord for not hesitating to answer our prayers and plans. Couldn’t have asked for a better Valentine’s gift.” Over the weekend she hinted the pregnancy news and shared a Bible verse. “When the time is right I, the Lord, will make it happen. Isaiah 60:22,” she wrote. ALSO READ : MASKANDI MBOKODOS RISE UP! At this stage it is not clear how far along she is in her pregnancy but she’s already showing. She also did not disclose who the father of the baby is. But her close friends and family have since flooded her comments’ section with congratulatory messages. Her twin sister, Brown Mbombo couldn’t be happier, she congratulated and said: “We’re having a baby.” Ziyanda posted: “Congratulations, Blue. We thank God Our Creator, praying for guidance and protection for you this day onwards. Super happy for you maarn.” While Thandiwe commented: “Thee best reveal so far...Very creative and unique...It’s nice to see people who think outside of the box. Congratulations!!” The most perfect valentines gift ??. Thank you Lord ?????? #mom2b #ValentinesDay2022 pic.twitter.com/IlHqy9aGpT 